flowchart TD
    DV[DEBUG_VECT diterima\nx=errorx  y=errory] --> SCALE[Skala ke radian\n× TRK_MAX_DEG × π/180]
    SCALE --> STORE[simpan _errorx_rad  _errory_rad]

    STORE --> UPD[update ~50 Hz]
    UPD --> TO{Sinyal timeout?}

    TO -- ya --> ZERO[nav_roll_cd = 0\nnav_pitch_cd = 0]

    TO -- tidak --> DB1{abs ex > TRK_DBAND?}
    DB1 -- tidak --> RI1[reset_I roll\nredaman laju gyro → nav_roll_cd]
    DB1 -- ya    --> RP[PID Roll\ndeg·ex → nav_roll_cd]

    RI1 --> DB2
    RP  --> DB2

    DB2{abs ey > TRK_DBAND?}
    DB2 -- tidak --> RI2[reset_I pitch\nnav_pitch_cd = 0]
    DB2 -- ya    --> PP[PID Pitch\ndeg·ey − TRK_PITCH_OFFSET → nav_pitch_cd]
